00:43.961 --> 00:45.628
Guys.

00:46.630 --> 00:49.799
[Man]
Making some new friends, Kurt?

00:49.883 --> 00:51.676
He sure is, Mr. Schue.

00:51.760 --> 00:54.679
Hey, Finn. You still owe me
that report on—
[Speaks Spanish]

00:54.805 --> 00:57.140
What?
What you did last summer.

00:57.224 --> 01:00.435
Almost halfway done with
almost all of it, Mr. Schue.

01:00.519 --> 01:02.854
- It's "Hammer time."
- Please. This is from
Marc Jacobs's new collection.

01:02.938 --> 01:04.439
Wait.

01:09.403 --> 01:11.571
Okay.

01:11.655 --> 01:13.865
♪ You're a shining star ♪

01:13.949 --> 01:15.450
♪ No matter who you are ♪

01:15.534 --> 01:18.453
[Bell Rings]
♪ Shining bright to see ♪

01:18.537 --> 01:21.914
